==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Puzzle-headed
<hw>Puz"zle-head`ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having the head full of
confused notions; given to getting perplexed over simple matters; also,
characteristic of persons that are so.</def>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

